qit]] <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.dundee.ac.uk/news/2017/dundee-clinician-scientist-receives-prestigious-medical-prize-.php | title=Dundee Clinician Scientist Receives Prestigious Medical Prize : News}}</ref> (planned) *2019 [[Mona Bafadhel]] ''Eosinophils in COPD: A breakthrough in patient management'' <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.medsci.ox.ac.uk/news/professor-bafadhel-receives-prestigious-royal-college-of-physicians-award | title=Professor Bafadhel receives prestigious Royal College of Physicians award: News}}</ref> (Feb 2019) * }}
